summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Sixty-fifth Street from 17th Avenue N.E. to 22nd Avenue N.E. et al in the City of Seattle, by laying water mains under Ordinance No. 17704 creating Local Improvement District No. 1681 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
